data.description: Have you been looking for something out in the country to have your very own hobby farm then look no further, this is the place for you! This charming property boasts a private gated entrance for ultimate privacy and security. Perfect for animal lovers, it features a spacious pig pen, a cozy chicken coop, and a fenced area for your beloved dogs to roam freely. Enjoy breathtaking views overlooking a picturesque 30-acre horse farm, providing a serene backdrop to your daily life. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, there's plenty of space for family and guests. The farmhouse kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with a classic cast iron stove, double oven & stainless steel appliances, real brick backsplash and pristine white cabinetry. Indulge in relaxation in the master bedroom with dual vanities and a luxurious large tile shower. The finished basement makes an ideal 4th bedroom, complete with a private entrance and stubbed for an additional bathroom, offering endless possibilities for customization. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your own private oasis where country living meets modern comfort.
